window.bookSummaryJSON = "<i>The Authoritarians</i> summarizes the research of Dr. Robert Altemeyer, whose professional career has focused on the study of the Authoritarian Personality, and development of the Right-Wing Authoritarian (RWA) personality and ideological variable widely studied in political, social, and personality psychology. <p>The foreword is provided by John W. Dean, former Nixon White House counsel and <i>New York Times</i> best-selling author.</p>"; 
